<subSubSection id="C30465748267131725A584B5FB41FDC2" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BA136FF8267131725A584B5FADBFE6E" blockId="68.[151,1436,438,643]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED8267131725A584B5FEA3FE53" bold="true" box="[151,273,438,463]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Chelicerae without intermarginal denticles; ventral opisthosoma pale in colour (
<figureCitation id="13252A7A82671317219284B5FAB6FE52" box="[1184,1284,438,462]" captionStart="FIGURE 58" captionStartId="90.[151,250,1810,1833]" captionTargetBox="[260,1377,264,1777]" captionTargetId="figure-62@90.[208,1378,229,1778]" captionTargetPageId="90" captionText="FIGURE 58. Habitus of species of the doriae group. (a–b) Eusparassus doriae (Simon, 1874) syntype female from Iran; (c) Eusparassus maynardi (Pocock, 1901) lectotype female from Pakistan; (d) Eusparassus fuscimanus Denis, 1958 female from Afghanistan; (e–f) Eusparassus oculatus (Kroneberg, 1875) female from Uzbekistan." pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Fig. 58b</figureCitation>
); ST small in size and located behind EM (e.g. 
<figureCitation id="13252A7A82671317273F84D9FDDFFE6E" box="[525,621,474,498]" captionStart="FIGURE 67" captionStartId="99.[151,250,1489,1512]" captionTargetBox="[172,1417,198,1468]" captionTargetId="figure-47@99.[151,1436,193,1469]" captionTargetPageId="99" captionText="FIGURE 67. Eusparassus doriae group. (a–b) Eusparassus doriae (Simon, 1874); (c–d) Eusparassus fuscimanus Denis, 1958; (e–f) Eusparassus kronebergi Denis, 1958. (a, c, e) left male palps, ventral; (b, d, f) epigynes, dorsal." pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Fig. 67a</figureCitation>
); AMLL of epigyne not fused anteriorly (e.g. 
<figureCitation id="13252A7A82671317214284D9FB63FE6E" box="[1136,1233,474,498]" captionStart="FIGURE 67" captionStartId="99.[151,250,1489,1512]" captionTargetBox="[172,1417,198,1468]" captionTargetId="figure-47@99.[151,1436,193,1469]" captionTargetPageId="99" captionText="FIGURE 67. Eusparassus doriae group. (a–b) Eusparassus doriae (Simon, 1874); (c–d) Eusparassus fuscimanus Denis, 1958; (e–f) Eusparassus kronebergi Denis, 1958. (a, c, e) left male palps, ventral; (b, d, f) epigynes, dorsal." pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Fig. 67b</figureCitation>
); GP present.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA136FF8267131725F584FDFB41FDC2" blockId="68.[151,1436,438,643]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED8267131725F584FDFE0DFD8B" bold="true" box="[199,447,510,535]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Species composition.</emphasis>
Seven species: 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D7C82671317274A84FCFBBBFD8A" authority="(Simon, 1874)" baseAuthorityName="Simon" baseAuthorityYear="1874" box="[632,1033,510,534]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="doriae">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED82671317274A84FCFCEAFD8A" box="[632,856,510,534]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Eusparassus doriae</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B0E82671317265B84FDFBB3FD8A" author="Simon, E." box="[873,1025,510,534]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" pagination="243 - 279" refId="ref52485" refString="Simon, E. (1874) Etudes arachnologiques. 3 e memoire. V. Revision des especes europeennes de la famille des Sparassidae. Annales de la Societe entomologique de France, Paris, 5 (4), 243 - 279." type="journal article" year="1874">Simon, 1874</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D7C82671317212584FCFAC7FD8A" authority="(Kroneberg, 1875)" baseAuthorityName="Kroneberg" baseAuthorityYear="1875" box="[1047,1397,510,534]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oculatus">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED82671317212584FCFB25FD8A" box="[1047,1175,510,534]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">E. oculatus</emphasis>
(Kroneberg, 1875)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D7C8267131720B684FCFE2DFDA6" authority="(Simon, 1895)" baseAuthorityName="Simon" baseAuthorityYear="1895" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="potanini">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED8267131720B684FCFF46FDA6" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">E. potanini</emphasis>
(Simon, 1895)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D7C8267131724988720FD55FDA6" authority="(Pocock, 1901)" baseAuthorityName="Pocock" baseAuthorityYear="1901" box="[426,743,546,571]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maynardi">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED8267131724988720FD81FDA7" box="[426,563,547,571]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">E. maynardi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B0E8267131727738721FD6DFDA6" author="Pocock, R. I." box="[577,735,546,570]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" pagination="478 - 498" refId="ref52017" refString="Pocock, R. I. (1901) Descriptions of some new species of spiders from British India. Journal of Bombay Natural History Society, 13, 478 - 498." type="journal article" year="1901">Pocock, 1901</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="4C1E4D7C8267131727C08720FBA8FDA6" authority="Denis, 1958" authorityName="Denis" authorityYear="1958" box="[754,1050,546,571]" class="Arachnida" family="Sparassidae" genus="Eusparassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kronebergi">
<emphasis id="B96AEAED8267131727C08720FC38FDA7" box="[754,906,547,571]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">E. kronebergi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B0E8267131726A28721FBA8FDA6" author="Denis, J." box="[912,1050,546,570]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" pagination="81 - 120" refId="ref50398" refString="Denis, J. (1958) Araignees (Araneidea) de l'Afghanistan. I. Videnskabelige Meddelelser fra Dansk naturhistorike Forenning, 120, 81 - 120." type="journal article" year="1958">Denis, 1958</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
