<bibRefCitation id="EF8F4B0E82671317273B8744FD3BFDC2" author="Jager, P." box="[521,649,582,607]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" pagination="37 - 57" refId="ref51040" refString="Jager, P. (2012) Revision of the genus Sinopoda Jager, 1999 in Laos with discovery of first eyeless huntsman spider species (Sparassidae: Heteropodinae). Zootaxa, 3415, 37 - 57." type="journal article" year="2012">Jäger, 2012</bibRefCitation>
